satori-sdk-java 1.0.2 API

Packages 
Package Description
com.satori.rtm
Provides high-level SDK API and the state machine to manage a connection state.
com.satori.rtm.auth
Classes to manage authentication and authorization.
com.satori.rtm.connection
Classes related to the RTM connection for sending and receiving PDUs and JSON serializer.
com.satori.rtm.model
Classes that represent JSON data models and exceptions as Protocol Data Units (PDU).
com.satori.rtm.transport
Classes related to WebSocket transport implementation.
com.satori.rtm.utils
Utility classes for the Java SDK.
